</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-grid"></div>
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>
  <div class="hero-glow2"></div>
  <div class="hero-badge"><div class="dot"></div> Now Accepting — Edition IV</div>
  <h1><span class="blue">MPR</span><br><span class="gold">KICK</span>OFF</h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Madrid's premier 7v7 football tournament. Compete for cash prizes. Prove your squad belongs at the top.</p>
  <p class="hero-location">📍 Madrid, Spain &nbsp;<em>— Est. 2023</em></p>
  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a class="btn-primary" href="#register">⚽ Register Your Team</a>
    <a class="btn-outline" href="#how">How It Works</a>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-hint"><span>Scroll</span><div class="scroll-arrow"></div></div>
</section>

<div class="stats-strip">
  <div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-num">3</div><div class="stat-label">Official Editions</div></div>
  <div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-num">24</div><div class="stat-label">Teams Competed</div></div>
  <div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-num">7v7</div><div class="stat-label">Format</div></div>
  <div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-num" style="color:var(--blue)">€$$</div><div class="stat-label">Cash Prizes Every Edition</div></div>
</div>

<div id="how">
  <div class="section-wrap">
    <span class="section-tag">⚽ How It Works</span>
    <h2>From Sign-Up to <span style="color:var(--gold)">Champion</span></h2>
    <p class="section-intro">Three steps stand between your squad and the prize. Each tournament runs as a single high-energy matchday in Madrid.</p>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step-card"><div class="step-num">01</div><div class="step-icon">📋</div><h3>Register Your Squad</h3><p>Sign up a team of 7–10 players and pay the entry fee to lock in your spot. Only 8 teams per edition — spots go fast.</p></div>
      <div class="step-card"><div class="step-num">02</div><div class="step-icon">🏟️</div><h3>Group Stage</h3><p>The 8 teams are divided into 2 groups of 4. Each team will play each other within their group. Every goal counts. Top teams 2 teams of each group advance to the knockout semi-finals.</p></div>
      <div class="step-card"><div class="step-num">03</div><div class="step-icon">🏆</div><h3>Finals & Cash</h3><p>Win the final and take all the prize money home. It's winner takes all — only the champions get paid.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="prizes-bg" id="prizes">
  <div class="section-wrap">
    <span class="section-tag">💰 Prize Pool</span>
    <h2>Play for <span style="color:var(--gold)">Real Money</span></h2>
    <p class="section-intro">The winner takes it all. No consolation prizes — only the champions walk away with cash. Every game matters.</p>
    <div class="prize-grid" style="display:flex;justify-content:center;">
      <div class="prize-card gold-card" style="max-width:380px;width:100%"><div class="prize-medal">🥇</div><div class="prize-place">Champions Only</div><div class="prize-amt">💶 CASH</div><div class="prize-note" style="color:var(--muted);margin-top:.8rem">Winner takes all — announced per edition. 2nd and 3rd place receive glory, not cash.</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div>
  <div class="section-wrap">
    <span class="section-tag">📋 Tournament Format</span>
    <h2>How <span style="color:var(--blue)">We Play</span></h2>
    <p class="section-intro">Everything you need to prepare your squad for matchday in Madrid.</p>
    <div class="format-grid">
      <div class="format-card"><div class="format-icon">⚽</div><h3>Match Rules</h3><ul class="flist"><li>7 players per side on the pitch</li><li>Squad of up to 10 (3 subs allowed)</li><li>20-minute halves — no half-time break</li><li>Offside rules do NOT apply</li><li>Fair play enforced</li><li>Referee decisions are final</li></ul></div>
      <div class="format-card"><div class="format-icon">🏟️</div><h3>Venue & Logistics</h3><ul class="flist"><li>Held in Madrid — venue confirmed per edition</li><li>All matches on artificial turf</li><li>Arrive 30 minutes before first kickoff</li><li>Matching kit or official jerseys required</li><li>Water and refreshments on site</li><li>Photos and highlights each edition</li></ul></div>
      <div class="format-card"><div class="format-icon">📊</div><h3>Group Stage Points</h3><ul class="flist"><li>Win = 3 pts · Draw = 1 pt · Loss = 0</li><li>All 8 teams play each other once</li><li>Top 4 advance to semi-finals</li><li>Tiebreaker: GD → Goals For → H2H</li></ul></div>
      <div class="format-card"><div class="format-icon">⚠️</div><h3>Eligibility</h3><ul class="flist"><li>Open to all amateur and recreational players</li><li>Minimum age: 18 years old</li><li>Entry fee required to confirm spot</li><li>8 teams maximum per edition</li><li>First come, first registered</li></ul></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="past-bg" id="history">
  <div class="section-wrap">
    <span class="section-tag">🏆 Tournament History</span>
    <h2>Our <span style="color:var(--gold)">3 Phases</span></h2>
    <p class="section-intro">Since 2025, MPR Kickoff has run three successful tournaments in Madrid — 8 teams each time, battling it out for cash and glory.</p>
